March gave me time to reflect & to align myself. I lost two people close to me. Being here reminded me that life is short & that you shouldn’t have permanent feelings & grudges about temporary things. It’s my last week here & work’s been good, can’t wait for it all to come out. 

Lastly, do things outside your comfort zone & go where you’re loved & appreciated ALWAYS!

April, let’s see what you’ve got for me 😉
Tried to catch some waves but they caught my ass 😂🏄🏽‍♂️
